ZH: 他整天都懒洋洋地躺在床上。
EN: He lies lazily in bed all day long.

ZH: 这只猫懒洋洋地躺在沙发上。
EN: The cat lazily lies on the couch.

ZH: 她的动作总是懒洋洋的。
EN: Her movements are always lazy.

ZH: 上课时他总是懒洋洋地打瞌睡。
EN: He always dozes off lazily during class.

ZH: 昨天的会议进行得很懒洋洋。
EN: The meeting yesterday was conducted in a lazy manner.

ZH: 她的笑容显得懒洋洋的。
EN: Her smile looks lazy.

ZH: 房间里气氛十分懒洋洋。
EN: The atmosphere in the room is very lazy.

ZH: 这个星期天过得很懒洋洋。
EN: This Sunday passed lazily.

ZH: 他工作总是懒洋洋的，效率很低。
EN: He always works lazily, with low efficiency.

ZH: 在沙滩上晒太阳是件很懒洋洋的事情。
EN: Sunbathing on the beach is a lazy thing to do.

ZH: 冬天的阳光总是懒洋洋地晒。
EN: The winter sun always shines lazily.

ZH: 她的反应总是懒洋洋的，不太积极。
EN: Her response is always lazy and not very proactive.

ZH: 懒洋洋的天气让人感到疲倦。
EN: The lazy weather makes people feel tired.

ZH: 她懒洋洋地拖着疲倦的身体去上班。
EN: She dragged her tired body lazily to work.

ZH: 学校里的猫总是懒洋洋地躺在阳光下。
EN: The cats in the school always lazily lie in the sun.

ZH: 在周末，他喜欢懒洋洋地看电视。
EN: On weekends, he likes to lazily watch TV.

ZH: 那只狗撒了一个懒洋洋的大懒腰。
EN: The dog stretched lazily, with a big yawn.

ZH: 老虎懒洋洋地躺在草地上晒太阳。
EN: The tiger lies lazily on the grass, soaking up the sun.

ZH: 她赖在床上懒洋洋地玩手机。
EN: She lazily plays with her phone while lying in bed.

ZH: 懒洋洋的夏日午后，人们都在避开烈日。
EN: In the lazy afternoon of summer, people avoid the scorching sun.
